<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">About Me</h2>

    <div class="bio reveal stagger-1">
      <h3>Who I Am</h3>
      <p>
        I am a passionate Bioinformatics student with a strong foundation in
        data management and analytics. My journey involves bridging the gap
        between biological sciences and computational methods to uncover
        meaningful insights from complex data sets.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently, I am expanding my expertise through academic projects and
        internships, focusing on developing efficient algorithms and data
        visualization tools for biological research.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="timeline reveal stagger-2">
        <h3>Education</h3>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="date">Sep 2022 – Jun 2024</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h4>Bachelor's Degree in Bioinformatics</h4>
            <span class="institution">ESCI-UPF</span>
            <p>Health Services, Allied Health, Health Sciences.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
              <i class="las la-language"></i> English
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="date">Sep 2024 – Present</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h4>Bachelor's Degree in Bioinformatics</h4>
            <span class="institution">Universitat Politècnica de Catalunya</span
            >
            <p>Bachelor’s degree in Bioinformatics jointly offered by UPC, UB, UAB and UPF, taught entirely in English. The program combines biology, mathematics, computer science and statistical modeling, with a strong focus on biomedical applications, genomics, machine learning and large-scale data analysis.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
              <i class="las la-tools"></i> Linux System Administration (Bash), RStudio, Pymol, Python, Data Analysis, SQL
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline reveal stagger-3">
        <h3>Experience</h3>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="date">Aug 2023 - Aug 2024</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h4>Sales Attendant</h4>
            <span class="institution">Barcelona Airport Duty-Free Shop</span>
            <p>Customer service and sales support.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
              <i class="las la-users"></i> Customer Service, English communication skills
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="date">Oct 2024 - Present</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h4>Data Management & Analytics Intern</h4>
            <span class="institution">NTT DATA - DM@C</span>
            <p>
              Data Management Intern working on metadata governance and large-scale data quality assessment, developing skills relevant to biological databases, reproducible pipelines, and high-volume bioinformatics datasets.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
              <i class="las la-database"></i> Oracle SQL Developer, Azure Functions (Python), Data Quality, Generative AI, Git, English
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: white;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .bio {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bio h3,
  .timeline h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-left: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -6px;
    top: 0;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .institution {
    display: block;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #636e72;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
